==Useful Info==
'''Midges''' were among the most insignificant of demons. With their fondness for [[blink]]ing, they were somewhat like [[crimson imp]]s that hit twice as hard, but did not regenerate. They could be found in [[the Abyss]], [[Pandemonium]], and the [[Hell]]s.

==Tips & Tricks==
None needed.

==History==
Midges were removed in [[0.11]].

